{"tid":1747861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳梅林卓悅匯商場天花板大面積墜落　幸無人員傷亡","createTime":"2019-11-23T11:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T12:15:16.000Z","uid":104804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"db53a383aab19894f6464b87a10658641f8217a5","tid":1747861,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDwZPLD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDwZPLD.jpg&h=3e90b280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據深圳新聞網報道，今天（22日）下午5點多，位於深圳梅林的卓悅匯商場大廳天花板大面積墜落，幸無人員傷亡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRkPsxw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRkPsxw.jpg&h=7e08c975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Py35Ljc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPy35Ljc.jpg&h=66f141cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pS54gqS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpS54gqS.jpg&h=10e21912&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80a47d8601fb561c1d80ed02765c8ba607622bce","tid":1747861,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:49:08.000Z","msg":"事發位置位於卓悅匯商場南門一樓，左邊為小米專賣店，右邊為優衣庫。現場視頻顯示，南門一樓天花板大面積發生垮塌，地面上滿是掉落的建築材料。<br />\n<br />\n有目擊者表示，當時下班，出了寫字樓就看到全是灰塵撲出來。後來才知道卓悅匯天花板掉了下來，幸虧沒壓到人。「有幾個小孩告訴我，他們剛從旁邊的梅麗小學放學，穿過卓悅匯回家。剛走到門口，上面就塌了，真的好危險，在生死邊緣走了一遭。」<br />\n<br />\n卓悅匯商場負責人介紹，事故未造成人員傷亡。此前，事發區域正在檢修，發現安全隱患後，及時疏散了人群。事發後，商場已將事發區域封鎖。事故原因尚在調查。"},{"pid":"9e9cf8cd9711ea121fdbfaee4e3d3005d630abf4","tid":1747861,"uid":335783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:50:18.000Z","msg":"支那日常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好先進"},{"pid":"ae05a7b5a2cb8596eccc0592b01002df7091b81c","tid":1747861,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:50:20.000Z","msg":"死100個即係冇死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9186ea00306dc44607d0d3558eb1b5e45f3b117","tid":1747861,"uid":1654,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:50:36.000Z","msg":"等睇官方澄清絕無此事，嚴厲譴責有人造謠生事，罪無可恕"},{"pid":"a7e9d5a939d7f6c68c1f690eae368e9c372256b5","tid":1747861,"uid":322937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:51:21.000Z","msg":"責唔死啲排隊等食海底撈既黑警"},{"pid":"6e1dfb40b3a380090ef111fcfa29d2b7012204e2","tid":1747861,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:51:32.000Z","msg":"商場自行裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351bef833abe184e855733d4a4a061b7bca0f910","tid":1747861,"uid":132256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:51:39.000Z","msg":"有請成龍"},{"pid":"719ddaeda6de4b6cf3c4ceca0ed6b70e430a835e","tid":1747861,"uid":334806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:51:40.000Z","msg":"可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19ed8e54dce82b49ae01285754c5da46563b405","tid":1747861,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:51:42.000Z","msg":"有冇00後新移民中頭獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76963a06f64919801c4bcc0f61b58d66ec19fe3","tid":1747861,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db53a383aab19894f6464b87a10658641f8217a5","tid":1747861,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDwZPLD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDwZPLD.jpg&h=3e90b280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據深圳新聞網報道，今天（22日）下午5點多，位於深圳梅林的卓悅匯商場大廳天花板大面積墜落，幸無人員傷亡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRkPsxw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRkPsxw.jpg&h=7e08c975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />